					<![CDATA[
						 <p>A little late to find this gem, but it is absolutely unnerving and I want more like it! I like the nursery rhyme you came up with as well and the fact that it actually sounds like something I'd expect of German children's stories (let's be honest, something like this isn't too surprising for the region). Combined with the audio, I think this is an excellent example of a piece intended to make the reader a little paranoid as they read.</p> <p>Take my +1, friend. You deserve it. Also, props to anyone who stumbles across the kawaii birb.</p> 
				 	]]>
